outfit_data.top: A ruby red velvet blouse with voluminous sleeves and a relaxed fit. The fabric is soft and luxurious, featuring subtle sheen that catches the light.
outfit_data.bottom: Emerald green corduroy wide-leg trousers. They have an elasticated waistband for comfort and a slightly cropped length, ending just above the ankle.
outfit_data.shoes: Sapphire blue suede Chelsea boots with a stacked heel.  The leather lining ensures comfort while adding a touch of sophistication.
outfit_data.extras: A chunky amethyst wool knit scarf draped loosely around the neck, paired with delicate gold hoop earrings.  A vintage-inspired tweed crossbody bag in topaz adds a touch of old-world glamour.
